==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oversow
<hw>O`ver*sow"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>ofersawan</ets>.]</ety> <def>To sow where something has already
been sown.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His enemy came and <qex>oversowed</qex> cockle among the
wheat.</q> <rj><qau>Matt. xiii. 25. (Douay Version).</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overspan</ent>⟦br⟧
